#

Savory Pork and Celery Stuffed Bell Peppers

$12.5
380 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeLow-CarbHigh-Protein

Tags:

Comfort FoodHealthy EatingFamily Meal

Description

Delicious bell peppers stuffed with a savory pork and celery mixture, embodying a perfect balance of flavor and nutrition.

Ingredients

  • Bell Peppers: 4 large
  • Ground Pork: 1 lb
  • Celery: 1 cup, finely chopped
  • Onion: 1 medium, diced
  • Garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Diced Tomatoes: 1 cup
  • Cumin: 1 tsp
  • Paprika: 1 tsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Cheddar Cheese: 1 cup, shredded (optional)
